WEBVTT

01:37.970 --> 01:40.979
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.060 --> 01:43.979
[Episode 2]

01:51.710 --> 01:53.039
Who are you looking for?

01:58.890 --> 01:59.590
Sorry.

01:59.590 --> 02:00.760
I got the wrong room.

02:04.150 --> 02:05.000
Yucheng!

02:06.640 --> 02:08.300
Was this lady looking for you?

02:10.310 --> 02:11.570
You seem a bit nervous.

02:19.270 --> 02:20.060
Who?

02:23.960 --> 02:24.840
Miyu?

02:26.240 --> 02:27.500
What are you two doing?

02:27.760 --> 02:28.630
Hot gossip

02:28.630 --> 02:29.840
in the early morning.

02:29.860 --> 02:30.920
So you're Mrs. Nie.

02:31.230 --> 02:32.790
Yucheng has told me about you.

02:32.790 --> 02:34.450
Have we met somewhere before?

02:36.240 --> 02:37.570
You go back in. Go.

02:37.870 --> 02:38.630
Don't get it wrong.

02:38.630 --> 02:40.360
This isn't what you think it is.

02:41.790 --> 02:43.280
Why did you push me in?

02:43.310 --> 02:45.120
I didn't finish talking to Mrs. Nie.

02:45.120 --> 02:46.020
Are you out of your mind?

02:46.020 --> 02:47.000
What are you afraid of?

02:47.000 --> 02:48.660
Why are you raising your voice?

02:48.660 --> 02:49.680
Do you want everyone to hear you?

02:49.680 --> 02:50.300
So what if they hear me?

02:50.300 --> 02:51.000
What's wrong with that?

02:51.000 --> 02:51.560
Can you just go in the room?

02:51.560 --> 02:52.400
Nie Yucheng!

02:52.400 --> 02:54.140
Did you tell me to come
so I could see this?

02:54.140 --> 02:54.700
No...

02:56.030 --> 02:57.280
Miyu. Miyu!

02:57.910 --> 02:59.040
Where are you going?

03:00.150 --> 03:01.010
Lu Zhenzhen...

03:02.490 --> 03:03.030
Miyu!

03:19.560 --> 03:20.540
Miyu!

03:21.550 --> 03:22.390
Miyu!

03:23.780 --> 03:24.930
Miyu!

03:56.590 --> 03:59.110
Low battery. Please replace batteries.

04:04.680 --> 04:06.840
These shampoos of yours work quite well.

04:06.840 --> 04:08.170
I'm taking them with me.

04:09.790 --> 04:12.580
Look how many pearl necklaces
you've bought.

04:13.850 --> 04:15.020
Do you even

04:15.040 --> 04:16.120
get to wear all of these?

04:16.120 --> 04:17.290
Take them if you like.

04:17.290 --> 04:18.950
I'll take them all then, okay?

04:19.730 --> 04:21.459
Why are you looking like this?

04:22.270 --> 04:23.130
Come over here.

04:23.350 --> 04:25.010
Let me see you in better light.

04:28.600 --> 04:29.200
Let me see.

04:32.150 --> 04:33.740
Look at yourself.

04:33.760 --> 04:35.640
You've got dark circles under your eyes.

04:35.640 --> 04:37.440
Fine lines are starting to grow.

04:37.590 --> 04:38.590
Listen up,

04:38.950 --> 04:40.830
you're not a young girl anymore.

04:40.990 --> 04:42.620
It's time you began
taking care of your skin.

04:42.620 --> 04:43.620
Got it?

04:44.000 --> 04:46.680
Low battery. Please replace batteries.

04:46.680 --> 04:47.940
Someone's at the door.

04:48.060 --> 04:48.770
Ignore it.

04:49.600 --> 04:50.760
Open up. It's me.

04:51.909 --> 04:52.680
It's Yucheng.

04:52.680 --> 04:54.280
-Go open the door!
-I'll do it.

04:54.280 --> 04:55.409
Don't open the door!

04:56.300 --> 04:58.950
-What happened? Did you get into a fight?
-Miyu! Open up, Miyu!

04:58.950 --> 05:02.040
-Whatever it is, sit down and talk to him.
-Don't butt in.

05:02.040 --> 05:03.900
-Just don't open the door.
-Miyu!

05:05.310 --> 05:06.430
It's me. Open the door!

05:06.430 --> 05:07.270
Miyu!

05:09.270 --> 05:10.240
It's high time we left.

05:10.240 --> 05:11.070
We've got things to do.

05:11.070 --> 05:11.830
Hurry up.

05:12.070 --> 05:12.390
Stop eating.

05:12.390 --> 05:13.680
Tidy up the table for your aunt.

05:13.680 --> 05:14.940
Hurry. Let me fix this.

05:19.430 --> 05:20.000
Well,

05:20.510 --> 05:21.510
we can't leave

05:21.510 --> 05:23.370
without opening the door, right?

05:27.270 --> 05:28.890
-You're back, Yucheng.
-Zhigang.

05:28.890 --> 05:29.690
Welcome back.

05:30.430 --> 05:31.000
Hand that to me.

05:31.000 --> 05:32.270
Let Zhigang carry it for you.

05:32.270 --> 05:33.270
Just put it there.

05:33.630 --> 05:34.680
My sister never stays mad for long.

05:34.680 --> 05:36.010
Just try to cheer her up.

05:36.520 --> 05:37.560
Why not stay for lunch

05:37.560 --> 05:38.680
before you leave?

05:38.680 --> 05:39.480
Sounds great.

05:40.680 --> 05:42.680
Then we can tell my sister and her husband

05:42.680 --> 05:44.270
what happened last night.

05:45.480 --> 05:46.430
A-Alright.

05:46.450 --> 05:48.940
We'd better stay out of your own business.

05:51.000 --> 05:52.240
Don't push your luck.

05:52.240 --> 05:54.680
Watch your mouth. Don't make things worse.

05:56.600 --> 05:57.750
We're getting going.

05:57.750 --> 05:58.480
Okay.

05:59.240 --> 06:00.160
No need to see us out.

06:00.160 --> 06:00.680
Really.

06:01.240 --> 06:02.160
Let's eat together some other day.

06:02.160 --> 06:02.720
Sure.

06:02.720 --> 06:04.320
Smooth things over with her.

06:04.490 --> 06:05.560
Take care!

06:05.600 --> 06:06.600
Let me carry this.

06:25.780 --> 06:26.240
Miyu...

06:26.240 --> 06:27.100
Don't touch me.

06:29.010 --> 06:30.210
I want a word with you.

06:30.230 --> 06:30.940
About what?

06:33.370 --> 06:34.770
About getting a divorce?

06:35.159 --> 06:35.800
No.

06:36.600 --> 06:38.150
You know I'll never walk out on you

06:38.150 --> 06:40.850
-or our home. Please hear me out...
-Then, yesterday,

06:40.850 --> 06:42.450
how did you leave this place?

06:42.730 --> 06:43.360
When you were

06:43.360 --> 06:45.360
intimate with another woman in bed,

06:45.920 --> 06:47.520
did you think about our home?

06:48.080 --> 06:49.340
Did you think about me?

06:50.230 --> 06:52.380
What happened yesterday
was not as ugly as you think.

06:52.380 --> 06:53.380
It really wasn't.

06:53.409 --> 06:54.480
Something must be wrong with that wine.

06:54.480 --> 06:54.920
Listen,

06:54.920 --> 06:56.600
-it must've been spiked. I fell...
-Nie Yucheng!

06:56.600 --> 06:58.250
-I fell unconscious after drinking it.
-What story are you making up now?

06:58.250 --> 06:59.040
Will you please hear me out?

06:59.040 --> 07:00.420
I'm not making up a story!

07:00.420 --> 07:01.250
Look.

07:01.090 --> 07:03.400
[Lu Zhenzhen, sales rep of Yuhua Hotel]

07:01.280 --> 07:02.360
This is my chat history

07:02.360 --> 07:03.610
with Lu Zhenzhen, alright?

07:03.610 --> 07:04.130
Look.

07:04.470 --> 07:04.920
She kept...

07:04.920 --> 07:06.160
-I don't want to watch this!
-She kept sending me messages.

07:06.160 --> 07:07.720
-My replies were plain and simple.
-I don't want to watch this!

07:07.720 --> 07:08.830
Will you just take a look?

07:08.830 --> 07:10.510
She knew I was at the hotel,

07:10.530 --> 07:11.360
so she asked to see me

07:11.360 --> 07:12.480
and show me a proposal.

07:12.480 --> 07:13.360
That's all there was to it.

07:13.360 --> 07:14.920
Now I feel sick just at the sight of you.

07:14.920 --> 07:15.920
I'm sorry. Sorry.

07:15.920 --> 07:16.930
I apologize to you.

07:16.930 --> 07:17.930
I did wrong.

07:17.960 --> 07:19.130
I'm regretting it, okay?

07:19.130 --> 07:20.450
Get lost!

08:10.300 --> 08:11.850
[Dad]

08:13.090 --> 08:14.430
Hey, Miyu.

08:13.250 --> 08:15.730
[Microphone On] [Speaker On] [Camera On]

08:14.560 --> 08:15.820
What are you doing?

08:16.010 --> 08:16.970
Dad, it's me.

08:17.020 --> 08:19.020
[Microphone On] [Speaker On] [Camera On]

08:17.990 --> 08:19.250
Oh, it's you, Yucheng.

08:19.300 --> 08:20.700
Why is it you on the phone?

08:22.550 --> 08:23.440
Thank you

08:23.470 --> 08:24.800
for buying me a new phone.

08:24.800 --> 08:26.260
It's working pretty well.

08:26.600 --> 08:27.240
Don't mention it.

08:27.240 --> 08:27.920
We're family.

08:27.920 --> 08:29.320
I'm just glad you like it.

08:31.980 --> 08:32.860
Miyu!

08:33.360 --> 08:34.480
I'm on a video call with Dad.

08:34.480 --> 08:35.270
Come out now.

08:36.600 --> 08:37.340
Miyu,

08:37.510 --> 08:38.840
Dad wants to talk to you.

08:39.789 --> 08:41.030
Why not come out?

08:44.360 --> 08:45.160
Miyu!

08:45.190 --> 08:45.790
Miyu...

08:45.810 --> 08:47.290
What happened to her? Is she okay?

08:47.290 --> 08:48.190
Nothing happened.

08:48.190 --> 08:48.790
She's just tired

08:48.790 --> 08:49.790
and feeling a bit unwell,

08:49.790 --> 08:51.070
so she's lying in bed in our bedroom.

08:51.070 --> 08:52.670
She'll be with us in a moment.

08:57.790 --> 08:59.360
Yes, we had a great time

08:59.360 --> 09:00.910
and took lots of photos.

09:01.790 --> 09:02.390
Dad, seriously,

09:02.390 --> 09:04.240
that hotel is exceptionally beautiful.

09:04.240 --> 09:05.890
Let me show you our guesthouse.

09:05.890 --> 09:06.580
Really?

09:06.690 --> 09:07.620
Let me see.

09:09.650 --> 09:10.480
Wait a second.

09:11.750 --> 09:13.480
Dad is showing us the Xu family inn.

09:13.480 --> 09:14.410
Come have a look.

09:14.920 --> 09:16.120
Dad, Miyu is here.

09:17.000 --> 09:18.360
Let me show you around.

09:19.790 --> 09:21.030
Look at the entrance.

09:21.150 --> 09:22.480
Impressive, huh?

09:23.240 --> 09:25.440
"Xu Family Inn."

09:26.080 --> 09:28.360
I specially asked Mr. Cao
to inscribe the sign.

09:28.360 --> 09:29.560
This cabinet right at the entrance

09:29.560 --> 09:30.750
was picked by Miyu.

09:31.920 --> 09:32.930
Here's a bonsai.

09:32.970 --> 09:34.520
Look at these decorations.

09:34.630 --> 09:35.760
Incredible, right?

09:36.930 --> 09:38.340
Listen,

09:38.480 --> 09:41.030
Miyu's interest in art has really

09:41.080 --> 09:42.270
come in handy.

09:42.700 --> 09:45.000
It's truly useful at critical moments.

09:45.030 --> 09:45.790
Right?

09:47.030 --> 09:47.630
By the way,

09:47.740 --> 09:48.460
well, we...

09:48.480 --> 09:50.650
genuinely hope you can refer as many

09:51.030 --> 09:52.970
tour groups as possible to our inn.

09:53.160 --> 09:55.690
The furnishings of this place

09:55.720 --> 09:57.150
are definitely the best

09:57.170 --> 09:58.840
for miles around.

09:58.870 --> 09:59.480
Rest assured.

09:59.480 --> 10:01.110
Visitors won't be disappointed
when they arrive.

10:01.110 --> 10:03.500
I don't need to conduct a quality check
before referring clients to you.

10:03.500 --> 10:04.500
We're family.

10:04.530 --> 10:06.190
Who else would I refer clients to,
if not you?

10:06.190 --> 10:06.980
That's right.

10:06.980 --> 10:07.780
We're family.

10:19.750 --> 10:21.000
Dad, how about this?

10:21.020 --> 10:23.230
I'll take a day of annual leave
in a few days

10:23.230 --> 10:24.510
and visit the family inn with Miyu,

10:24.510 --> 10:25.120
okay?

10:25.390 --> 10:26.320
Sure.

10:26.470 --> 10:27.390
I'll cook something nice

10:27.390 --> 10:29.030
for you when you're here.

10:29.270 --> 10:30.630
Yucheng, you love

10:30.630 --> 10:32.280
the ornamental pastries I make,

10:32.280 --> 10:33.070
don't you?

10:33.370 --> 10:35.530
My mouth is watering upon hearing it.

10:35.630 --> 10:38.030
Shall we pay a visit this weekend?

10:39.610 --> 10:40.740
Get your hand off me.

10:42.550 --> 10:43.300
Miyu,

10:43.360 --> 10:44.510
Yucheng's talking to you nicely.

10:44.510 --> 10:45.270
Why do you have to take

10:45.270 --> 10:46.600
this attitude with him?

10:46.880 --> 10:49.080
Don't throw temper tantrums, alright?

10:49.840 --> 10:50.480
Mom, Dad,

10:50.480 --> 10:51.480
you're mistaken.

10:51.480 --> 10:52.960
We just got back from abroad.

10:52.960 --> 10:53.720
Miyu was unpacking

10:53.720 --> 10:54.550
and probably got tired.

10:54.550 --> 10:55.680
Everything's fine.

10:55.720 --> 10:56.600
You guys talk.

10:56.720 --> 10:57.720
I'll go cook.

11:32.440 --> 11:34.080
Yucheng, well...

11:34.120 --> 11:36.530
If there's a problem, talk it through.

11:36.640 --> 11:37.840
I know best about

11:37.840 --> 11:39.360
my daughter's temper.

11:39.360 --> 11:40.840
Her anger never lasts long.

11:40.840 --> 11:41.720
A few days, at most.

11:41.720 --> 11:42.840
Okay. I'll talk to her.

11:42.840 --> 11:43.720
Don't worry.

11:43.840 --> 11:45.240
Every problem can be solved.

11:45.240 --> 11:46.690
I have faith in Yucheng.

11:47.000 --> 11:48.410
You're a brilliant young man.

11:48.410 --> 11:50.960
Alright. Go back to what you were doing.

11:51.020 --> 11:52.420
We'd hate to disturb you.

11:52.480 --> 11:53.610
Take care, Mom, Dad.

11:53.660 --> 11:54.320
I'm hanging up now.

11:54.320 --> 11:55.320
-Bye.
-Okay, bye.

12:02.860 --> 12:03.610
[Dad]

12:03.670 --> 12:04.530
[WeChat]

12:06.290 --> 12:07.120
[Honey]

12:07.180 --> 12:07.810
[WeChat]

12:07.840 --> 12:08.540
[Babe, send the blue shirt I usually wear]

12:08.570 --> 12:09.290
[to Room 1819, Purong Hotel,
at 6:00 tomorrow]

12:09.310 --> 12:10.030
[No need to reply. Love you]

12:15.380 --> 12:17.390
[Honey]

12:18.840 --> 12:19.330
[Babe, send the blue shirt I usually wear]

12:19.350 --> 12:19.890
[to Room 1819, Purong Hotel,
at 6:00 tomorrow]

12:25.920 --> 12:26.400
Mom.

12:26.530 --> 12:27.260
Yucheng,

12:27.450 --> 12:30.260
I'd like to speak to Miyu.

12:30.820 --> 12:31.720
Sure. Just a moment.

12:31.720 --> 12:33.180
I'll pass the phone to her.

12:39.120 --> 12:40.320
What's wrong with me?

12:42.700 --> 12:43.540
Miyu.

12:45.180 --> 12:46.580
Mom wants to speak to you.

12:50.990 --> 12:51.650
Mom.

12:51.730 --> 12:52.540
Miyu,

12:53.200 --> 12:55.920
your sister told me everything
when she came back.

12:55.920 --> 12:58.120
I know you got into a fight with Yucheng.

12:58.480 --> 12:59.670
I already noticed that

12:59.670 --> 13:01.200
on the previous video call.

13:01.510 --> 13:02.670
When you're mad,

13:02.920 --> 13:05.360
sulk or throw a tantrum as you like.

13:06.120 --> 13:06.840
However,

13:07.010 --> 13:08.610
don't get out of line.

13:08.900 --> 13:09.690
Mom,

13:10.080 --> 13:11.120
you have no idea.

13:11.870 --> 13:12.390
Nie Yucheng actually...

13:12.390 --> 13:13.250
I know.

13:13.280 --> 13:14.760
I know how you must feel.

13:15.440 --> 13:16.790
He has upset you.

13:17.120 --> 13:19.090
But you must be clear about one thing.

13:19.090 --> 13:21.810
That is, your husband
is providing for you now.

13:22.440 --> 13:23.720
No matter what has happened,

13:23.720 --> 13:24.480
just sit down,

13:24.480 --> 13:26.950
talk it through,
and the problem will go away.

13:26.950 --> 13:28.000
I saw how Nie Yucheng

13:28.000 --> 13:30.250
treated you just now.

13:30.280 --> 13:31.950
He was talking sweet to you, wasn't he?

13:31.950 --> 13:34.070
If he intended to leave you,

13:34.090 --> 13:35.240
he would just ignore you

13:35.240 --> 13:37.210
no matter how you tried to sweet talk him.

13:37.210 --> 13:38.820
How could you say that, Mom?

13:38.970 --> 13:40.370
My words may sound harsh,

13:40.630 --> 13:42.820
but they're all for your own good.

13:42.950 --> 13:44.190
Think about it.

13:44.210 --> 13:46.860
Given Yucheng's current wealth
and social status,

13:46.860 --> 13:49.740
plus his car and house in Shanghai,

13:50.210 --> 13:51.840
a great number of temptresses

13:51.840 --> 13:53.480
are eager to take your place.

13:54.030 --> 13:55.540
What will become of you

13:55.560 --> 13:56.800
if you fall out with him?

13:56.800 --> 13:58.660
Have you ever thought about that?

13:58.660 --> 14:00.190
I've been where you are now.

14:01.200 --> 14:02.600
Having someone to rely on

14:02.720 --> 14:05.120
is better than suffering alone out there.

14:05.320 --> 14:06.840
Don't act silly.

14:06.870 --> 14:08.800
Don't give away your lovely home

14:08.820 --> 14:10.340
to someone else.

14:10.960 --> 14:13.270
Besides, get pregnant soon.

14:14.190 --> 14:15.280
Do you hear me?

14:21.500 --> 14:22.380
Yes.

14:54.990 --> 14:55.350
[Jane]

14:56.420 --> 14:58.490
[Photos and videos]

15:02.100 --> 15:04.100
Lu Zhenzhen, you tricked me?

15:21.870 --> 15:22.610
[Jane]

15:25.020 --> 15:26.960
You'd better give me a good reason.

15:42.360 --> 15:43.440
I'm pregnant.

16:23.250 --> 16:23.890
Miyu?

17:44.720 --> 17:45.890
I heated some milk for you.

17:45.890 --> 17:47.010
Drink it when you get up.

17:47.010 --> 17:47.940
Love you, Honey.

17:54.990 --> 17:58.600
[Changyang Travel]

17:56.030 --> 17:57.830
I heard that this business trip

17:57.930 --> 17:58.680
happened to

17:58.680 --> 18:00.830
coincide with
your 10th wedding anniversary.

18:00.830 --> 18:02.480
Your wife traveled all the way abroad

18:02.480 --> 18:03.830
to surprise you, didn't she?

18:03.830 --> 18:04.560
Yes, she did.

18:05.070 --> 18:06.480
We had no choice.

18:06.590 --> 18:08.400
After all,
the luxury wilderness overseas tours

18:08.400 --> 18:09.510
are the company's most important

18:09.510 --> 18:11.200
strategic plan for the next few years.

18:11.200 --> 18:12.050
In fact, Miyu

18:12.110 --> 18:13.770
is very supportive of my work.

18:14.350 --> 18:15.310
You truly married

18:15.310 --> 18:16.590
the right woman,

18:16.830 --> 18:17.750
for she brings you good fortune.

18:17.750 --> 18:19.030
You must cherish her.

18:19.030 --> 18:19.720
I know.

18:19.720 --> 18:20.520
I surely will.

18:21.030 --> 18:23.030
Any updates on the Svelto Hotel Group?

18:23.030 --> 18:24.550
Everything's going smoothly.

18:24.550 --> 18:25.960
Since the hotel's general manager there

18:25.960 --> 18:26.890
is also Chinese,

18:27.110 --> 18:29.720
there's no cultural barrier
in communication at all.

18:29.720 --> 18:31.690
We'll set up a group and connect online
next week

18:31.690 --> 18:32.720
for a formal meeting.

18:32.720 --> 18:33.510
This overseas project

18:33.510 --> 18:34.640
is a long-term endeavor.

18:34.640 --> 18:36.240
I believe in your abilities.

18:36.350 --> 18:39.000
But, as for the Yufeng Jiangnan project,

18:39.000 --> 18:40.660
I hope you'll give it your all.

18:41.350 --> 18:42.810
Just between you and me,

18:42.870 --> 18:44.530
the position of vice president

18:44.530 --> 18:46.640
will either be yours or Yin's.

18:47.030 --> 18:48.960
The others are no match for you.

18:49.550 --> 18:50.920
You know who's backing Yin

18:50.920 --> 18:52.310
without me saying, right?

18:52.310 --> 18:53.030
Yes, I do.

18:53.030 --> 18:55.960
You'll have more leverage
as long as you nail

18:55.960 --> 18:58.510
the Yufeng Jiangnan project.

18:58.530 --> 19:00.850
By then, however powerful
his connections are,

19:00.850 --> 19:01.920
he can't beat you.

19:04.550 --> 19:05.960
Thanks for the advice, Mr. Hu.

19:05.960 --> 19:07.490
I'll definitely do my best.

19:10.790 --> 19:14.760
[Yuhua Hotel]

19:23.770 --> 19:24.650
Hello, ma'am.

19:26.180 --> 19:26.640
Hello.

19:26.640 --> 19:28.260
I'm here to meet Lu Zhenzhen
from the sales department.

19:28.260 --> 19:29.790
Okay. Please wait a moment.

19:33.000 --> 19:34.110
A lady at the reception

19:34.110 --> 19:36.340
is asking to meet Lu Zhenzhen from sales.

19:36.340 --> 19:38.020
How may I address you, ma'am?

19:40.590 --> 19:41.480
Lu Zhenzhen, listen,

19:41.480 --> 19:42.480
my surname is Xu.

19:42.750 --> 19:44.390
I'll be waiting for you
at the coffee spot across the street.

19:44.390 --> 19:45.880
Meet me there in 30 minutes,

19:45.880 --> 19:48.010
or you'll bear serious consequences.

20:30.950 --> 20:31.880
Why are you so late?

20:31.880 --> 20:32.960
The traffic was terrible today.

20:32.960 --> 20:34.480
That's why I'm late.

20:45.760 --> 20:46.720
What's going on?

20:48.890 --> 20:51.150
Why hasn't the payment been settled yet?

20:51.810 --> 20:53.940
How am I supposed to pay the suppliers?

20:54.670 --> 20:55.910
Rush them, okay?

20:57.480 --> 20:58.240
Talking to Mr. Nie

20:58.240 --> 20:59.770
or Feng Bin won't be of help.

20:59.830 --> 21:00.660
That's it.

21:06.980 --> 21:09.490
Sorry to keep you waiting.

21:16.730 --> 21:17.860
What a coincidence.

21:17.950 --> 21:19.750
Our purses are exactly the same.

21:21.130 --> 21:23.460
I'm not here to talk about purses
with you.

21:24.590 --> 21:26.250
That was just an opening line.

21:26.430 --> 21:28.370
Why create so much tension?

21:28.800 --> 21:29.880
I was going to compliment you

21:29.880 --> 21:31.350
on your taste, Mrs. Nie.

21:32.130 --> 21:33.910
Leather and jewelry.

21:34.590 --> 21:36.590
Wild and elegant.

21:37.830 --> 21:39.370
But this combination doesn't

21:39.370 --> 21:41.030
really pair with your outfit.

21:41.500 --> 21:42.900
A bit too rigid, isn't it?

21:43.230 --> 21:45.890
These opening lines of yours
are not quite good.

21:46.840 --> 21:48.170
Who bought you this bag?

21:49.390 --> 21:50.870
Can't I buy it myself?

21:55.590 --> 21:56.350
Waitress.

21:56.740 --> 21:57.940
We're ready to order.

22:01.760 --> 22:02.640
I'll have a...

22:02.640 --> 22:04.440
I'll have a lemonade, thank you.

22:08.070 --> 22:08.870
I'll go with this one.

22:08.870 --> 22:10.500
Fantasy of the Deep Forest.

22:10.520 --> 22:11.520
Okay, ma'am.

22:17.510 --> 22:19.970
[Yuhua Hotel Frequent Guest Program]

22:30.640 --> 22:31.350
Go ahead.

22:31.830 --> 22:33.230
Why did you want to see me?

22:33.750 --> 22:35.120
Didn't you ask to see me?

22:45.640 --> 22:48.570
You sent me Wechat messages
from my husband's phone.

22:48.640 --> 22:50.970
Wasn't that just an excuse
to get to see me?

22:52.270 --> 22:53.790
Mrs. Nie, I think you may have

22:53.790 --> 22:54.880
misunderstood those messages.

22:54.880 --> 22:56.070
Then what's the truth?

22:56.070 --> 22:57.310
Didn't your husband tell you?

22:57.310 --> 22:58.750
What my husband tells me

22:58.750 --> 23:00.400
is between the two of us.

23:00.680 --> 23:02.680
I want to hear your side of the story.

23:02.960 --> 23:04.690
How did you two know each other?

23:04.750 --> 23:05.750
You mean Mr. Nie?

23:06.440 --> 23:08.110
We met through work. That's all.

23:08.110 --> 23:09.920
What kind of work is so complicated

23:09.920 --> 23:12.380
that it needs to be settled
in his hotel room?

23:12.510 --> 23:13.680
Mrs. Nie.

23:13.840 --> 23:15.600
I'm just an employee.

23:15.840 --> 23:17.640
If a client picks the place,

23:18.040 --> 23:19.210
I show up. Simple as that.

23:19.210 --> 23:20.540
So you're saying...

23:21.310 --> 23:23.030
Nie Yucheng was the one
who approached you first?

23:23.030 --> 23:24.200
I never said that.

23:24.920 --> 23:26.180
Mrs. Nie, please don't

23:26.980 --> 23:28.040
get the wrong idea.

23:28.500 --> 23:29.640
I don't want to cause

23:29.640 --> 23:31.710
any misunderstandings
between you and yoru husband.

23:31.710 --> 23:34.970
The last thing I need is to look like
I'm stirring things up.

23:35.840 --> 23:37.630
Sorry, I need to take this call.

23:41.440 --> 23:42.350
Hello, Mr. Yang.

23:42.350 --> 23:43.350
This is Zhenzhen.

23:43.470 --> 23:44.270
What's wrong?

23:45.270 --> 23:47.470
The payment still hasn't gone through?

23:50.200 --> 23:52.330
I'll go see Mr. Nie in person tomorrow.

23:53.110 --> 23:54.110
Don't worry.

23:54.110 --> 23:56.520
I'll get that money back,
even if I have to fight for it.

23:56.520 --> 23:57.680
I'm with a client right now.

23:57.680 --> 23:59.280
Can we talk about this later?

24:07.020 --> 24:07.740
Mrs. Nie.

24:08.670 --> 24:10.270
I came here today

24:10.400 --> 24:11.770
not because I'm afraid of you.

24:11.770 --> 24:13.130
I just want to remind you

24:13.240 --> 24:15.040
to mind your social boundaries.

24:15.200 --> 24:16.750
If a man makes a mistake,

24:16.750 --> 24:18.510
you should settle scores with him.

24:18.510 --> 24:20.000
Don't you think going after the woman

24:20.000 --> 24:21.370
is a bit low?

24:21.480 --> 24:23.340
Don't try to bluff your way out.

24:23.560 --> 24:25.690
I called you here to remind you as well.

24:25.700 --> 24:27.200
When you're dealing
with someone else's husband,

24:27.200 --> 24:28.960
you should also
mind your social boundaries.

24:28.960 --> 24:31.420
Being competitive at work
is your strength.

24:31.940 --> 24:33.200
But in relationships,

24:33.510 --> 24:35.200
snatching whatever you see

24:35.840 --> 24:37.480
is nothing but shameless.

24:40.780 --> 24:42.780
Are you saying I stole your husband?

24:42.840 --> 24:44.720
Then let me ask you, Mrs. Nie.

24:44.840 --> 24:46.400
If a man doesn't love me,

24:47.120 --> 24:48.880
why would I even bother?

24:49.710 --> 24:52.560
It takes two to tango.

24:53.240 --> 24:54.720
A man changing his mind

24:54.750 --> 24:56.750
is as common as upgrading a phone.

24:57.000 --> 24:58.560
That's just how it is.

24:59.550 --> 25:00.680
But I suppose

25:00.680 --> 25:02.340
that's a little unfair to you.

25:03.070 --> 25:04.130
You have no income,

25:04.570 --> 25:05.960
no status in the family,

25:05.990 --> 25:07.790
and no social circle of your own.

25:07.810 --> 25:08.970
If it came to divorce,

25:08.970 --> 25:11.120
you'd be the one at a disadvantage.

25:17.280 --> 25:18.480
Since this is our first meeting,

25:18.480 --> 25:20.410
and you've been so upfront with me,

25:20.530 --> 25:22.340
I'll give you some advice too.

25:22.840 --> 25:24.170
I don't have a job,

25:24.960 --> 25:27.350
so maybe I don't get
how things work in your world.

25:27.350 --> 25:28.240
However,

25:29.240 --> 25:31.350
I've been married
to Nie Yucheng for 10 years.

25:31.350 --> 25:32.240
I know him.

25:32.710 --> 25:34.070
Based on what you know about him—

25:34.070 --> 25:35.180
tell me,

25:35.210 --> 25:37.310
if he had to choose

25:37.310 --> 25:39.070
between you and his reputation,

25:39.070 --> 25:40.670
which do you think he'd pick?

25:41.880 --> 25:43.170
What do you mean?

25:43.750 --> 25:45.610
You set me up to catch him cheating

25:45.670 --> 25:48.350
just because you're desperate
to replace me, right?

25:48.350 --> 25:50.740
You couldn't make any progress
with Nie Yucheng,

25:50.740 --> 25:52.800
so now you're coming after me, right?

25:53.980 --> 25:55.380
I've got nothing to lose.

25:56.030 --> 25:56.890
What about you?

25:57.070 --> 25:58.600
You know better than anyone

25:58.880 --> 26:00.210
how easily men

26:00.310 --> 26:01.950
change their minds.

26:02.310 --> 26:04.640
So what makes you think he'd ruin himself,

26:04.750 --> 26:07.010
and bear the cheater label, just for you?

26:07.240 --> 26:09.000
I've heard plenty of

26:09.000 --> 26:10.590
harsh truths in my life.

26:11.550 --> 26:13.010
I only believe in one rule:

26:13.910 --> 26:15.310
survival of the fittest.

26:16.420 --> 26:17.630
It's that simple.

26:25.670 --> 26:27.270
Then I hope you keep winning.

26:28.850 --> 26:30.860
And if you ever lose,

26:31.120 --> 26:33.320
I hope you remember what you said today.

26:34.170 --> 26:35.430
I'll be waiting to see.

26:52.810 --> 26:55.020
[Nie Yucheng]

26:53.350 --> 26:54.880
Has the cat got your tongue?

27:12.230 --> 27:14.880
I called Lu Zhenzhen's bluffing,

27:14.910 --> 27:16.870
but wasn't I doing the same?

27:17.840 --> 27:19.470
Winning an argument

27:20.070 --> 27:22.530
doesn't change the fact
that I was betrayed.

27:23.950 --> 27:25.510
In this war,

27:26.830 --> 27:28.150
there are no winners.

27:57.880 --> 27:58.880
Don't come in yet.

28:00.430 --> 28:01.630
It's a mess in here.

28:01.950 --> 28:03.240
Watch your feet.

28:03.810 --> 28:05.220
I was trying to cook something for you,

28:05.220 --> 28:07.180
but I messed it up.

28:24.260 --> 28:24.720
Hello?

28:25.310 --> 28:26.770
The time can't be changed.

28:27.030 --> 28:28.550
This is their last chance.

28:28.880 --> 28:30.340
We have to hold our ground.

28:30.960 --> 28:32.270
I'll talk to Mr. Wang.

28:35.060 --> 28:36.990
Don't bring up Yuhua again. Got it?

28:38.270 --> 28:39.030
Okay, got it.

28:39.670 --> 28:41.130
I'm with my wife right now.

28:42.240 --> 28:43.180
How about this—

28:43.550 --> 28:45.790
get the project team together later.

28:45.790 --> 28:47.000
Let's do a quick meeting.

28:47.000 --> 28:48.400
Alright. I'm hanging up.

28:55.070 --> 28:56.310
Why are you home?

28:57.640 --> 28:59.390
Where else would I go?

28:59.510 --> 29:00.510
This is my home—

29:01.160 --> 29:02.190
our home.

29:03.070 --> 29:06.400
Don't you want me to come home early,
spending time with you?

29:13.060 --> 29:14.450
Don't bother cooking.

29:14.510 --> 29:16.720
We can order in or go out.

29:18.580 --> 29:19.840
Let's just eat at home.

29:20.390 --> 29:21.520
It'll be ready soon.

29:43.830 --> 29:46.070
Aren't you going to ask
where I went today?

29:46.070 --> 29:47.330
Where did you go today?

29:47.640 --> 29:49.040
I went to see Lu Zhenzhen.

29:57.590 --> 29:59.270
That woman is a compulsive liar.

29:59.270 --> 30:00.190
Why did you go see her?

30:00.190 --> 30:01.650
I'm not so sure about that.

30:02.000 --> 30:02.590
At least I know

30:02.590 --> 30:03.590
her limited edition

30:03.590 --> 30:05.440
designer bag is real.

30:06.000 --> 30:07.570
That was a gift from our company.

30:07.570 --> 30:09.500
I only suggested the brand.

30:09.720 --> 30:10.990
Who bought you this bag?

30:10.990 --> 30:12.270
Can't I buy it myself?

30:13.200 --> 30:14.200
My relationship with her

30:14.200 --> 30:15.310
isn't what you think.

30:15.310 --> 30:16.030
Really?

30:16.510 --> 30:18.000
So I'm the one with the dirty mind?

30:18.000 --> 30:19.270
What do you mean by that?

30:19.270 --> 30:20.510
I mean,

30:20.790 --> 30:23.520
people like you who have
a spark in the workplace—

30:23.790 --> 30:24.990
you're not cheaters.

30:25.310 --> 30:26.710
You're partners in arms,

30:27.160 --> 30:27.820
right?

30:31.480 --> 30:32.510
Maybe I've been

30:32.510 --> 30:33.970
stuck at home for too long,

30:34.350 --> 30:36.280
I've watched too many soap operas.

30:36.540 --> 30:38.200
When my husband cheated on me,

30:38.750 --> 30:40.920
I assumed it must be
some cheap floozy

30:40.920 --> 30:43.000
who seduced him with her beauty.

30:44.930 --> 30:46.210
How shallow of me.

30:48.750 --> 30:49.960
I can't even imagine

30:49.960 --> 30:51.970
how the two of you work together,

30:52.350 --> 30:53.810
or how deep that bond goes.

30:54.200 --> 30:56.310
All that unspoken tension,

30:56.510 --> 30:57.570
all that friction—

30:57.910 --> 30:59.900
they're way beyond my imagination.

30:59.900 --> 31:01.700
Because I've never had a career.

31:02.600 --> 31:04.810
Career women aren't anything special.

31:04.940 --> 31:06.660
It's just a job.

31:07.380 --> 31:09.030
Think about yourself back then.

31:09.030 --> 31:09.790
You gave up

31:10.220 --> 31:11.430
your career for me,

31:11.450 --> 31:12.640
and chose our family instead.

31:12.640 --> 31:14.750
That's what it means
to fight side by side,

31:14.750 --> 31:16.310
and share the same fate.

31:16.920 --> 31:18.270
Miyu, remember this—

31:18.640 --> 31:19.870
you are my wife.

31:20.510 --> 31:21.840
That will never change.

31:22.550 --> 31:23.070
Never?

31:23.090 --> 31:25.290
At least that's how I feel.

31:30.900 --> 31:32.830
Then whose red underwear was that?

31:33.310 --> 31:34.200
Was it hers?

31:36.560 --> 31:37.430
Was it?

31:41.790 --> 31:42.790
Some things

31:43.030 --> 31:44.430
are better left unknown.

31:46.510 --> 31:47.510
So it was hers.

31:55.970 --> 31:56.900
Fine. I admit it.

31:57.210 --> 31:58.610
She did come to see me.

31:58.630 --> 31:59.900
But I kicked her out.

31:59.960 --> 32:00.510
I never thought

32:00.510 --> 32:02.440
she'd pull a dirty trick like that.

32:02.590 --> 32:03.240
I never thought...

32:03.240 --> 32:05.500
So before I got to the Svelto Hotel Group—

32:05.550 --> 32:07.270
where was she those days?

32:07.270 --> 32:09.430
Was she with you the whole time?

32:09.480 --> 32:11.270
Sure, let me check the room availability.

32:11.270 --> 32:11.920
Okay.

32:15.270 --> 32:16.540
Is there a problem?

32:16.580 --> 32:17.940
Did you change rooms?

32:19.620 --> 32:20.250
Mrs. Nie.

32:20.680 --> 32:22.590
Mr. Nie is a VIP guest at our hotel.

32:22.590 --> 32:24.350
We just upgraded his room

32:24.370 --> 32:25.400
to a suite this morning.

32:25.400 --> 32:26.880
But we've already

32:26.880 --> 32:27.570
looked into this thoroughly.

32:27.570 --> 32:28.690
This is entirely

32:28.720 --> 32:30.350
our hotel's responsibility.

32:30.350 --> 32:31.240
So, Mrs. Nie,

32:31.240 --> 32:32.440
please rest assured.

32:41.790 --> 32:42.510
Miyu.

32:43.030 --> 32:45.030
I admit she came to see me those days.

32:45.070 --> 32:46.570
But I swear to you,

32:46.790 --> 32:48.750
we did nothing but work.

32:48.790 --> 32:50.200
Nothing happened.

32:50.200 --> 32:50.930
Understand?

32:51.420 --> 32:52.830
That must've been so hard for you.

32:52.830 --> 32:54.490
Working yourself to the bone,

32:54.510 --> 32:56.270
and still colluding
with the Svelto Hotel Group's

32:56.270 --> 32:57.270
general manager

32:57.890 --> 32:58.920
to lie to me

32:59.420 --> 33:00.820
and cover up your affair.

33:01.390 --> 33:03.320
Birds of a feather flock together.

33:04.810 --> 33:05.570
Miyu.

33:05.940 --> 33:07.740
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

33:08.660 --> 33:10.320
I just didn't want to hurt you.

33:10.510 --> 33:11.790
Lu Zhenzhen is

33:11.790 --> 33:14.000
trying to destroy our family deliberately.

33:14.000 --> 33:15.070
I was scared you'd fall for her tricks.

33:15.070 --> 33:16.130
Do you understand?

33:21.510 --> 33:23.110
You don't believe me, do you?

33:24.450 --> 33:28.050
[Lu Zhenzhen, Yuhua Hotel's Sales Rep]

33:24.880 --> 33:25.750
Lu Zhenzhen—

33:26.550 --> 33:28.080
I'm deleting her right now.

33:28.510 --> 33:30.720
She's out of our lives. For good.

33:31.510 --> 33:33.510
If she ever contacts me again,

33:33.770 --> 33:34.970
I'll talk to her supervisor

33:34.970 --> 33:35.970
and get her fired.

33:36.610 --> 33:38.050
[Friend Settings]

33:38.130 --> 33:39.470
[Delete Contact] [Delete]

33:39.270 --> 33:40.000
Deleted.

33:39.550 --> 33:40.480
[Please wait a moment]

33:40.540 --> 33:40.720
[Friend Settings]

33:41.280 --> 33:42.000
Miyu.

33:42.880 --> 33:44.710
Listen to me. Listen to me.

33:44.960 --> 33:46.720
I won't let anyone hurt you.

33:47.420 --> 33:50.030
You have to believe me on this.

33:57.760 --> 33:58.750
Ms. Lu,

33:58.790 --> 34:00.380
don't put me in a tough spot, okay?

34:00.380 --> 34:02.030
Really, if there's anything, just tell me.

34:02.030 --> 34:04.510
-How many times have I told you? Did it work?
-Let me help you.

34:04.510 --> 34:07.510
-Ms. Lu, Mr. Nie is…
-Don't mind me, just do your thing.

34:13.100 --> 34:14.750
[Yuhua Hotel Co., Ltd.
Statement of Account]

34:17.920 --> 34:19.000
Go find Feng Bin.

34:19.550 --> 34:20.810
He's in charge of this.

34:21.440 --> 34:23.810
Feng Bin has been stalling us
for three weeks straight.

34:23.810 --> 34:25.290
I had no choice but to come to you.

34:25.290 --> 34:25.929
Mr. Nie,

34:26.020 --> 34:27.550
let's keep personal and work separate.

34:27.550 --> 34:28.980
I won't pressure you about the baby,

34:28.980 --> 34:30.670
so don't make things hard for me at work,

34:30.670 --> 34:31.280
okay?

34:48.750 --> 34:49.949
How are you feeling?

34:52.630 --> 34:53.670
I'm fine.

34:54.120 --> 34:55.920
I just throw up everything I eat.

34:57.590 --> 34:58.420
I'm sorry.

34:58.710 --> 35:00.310
I've put you through so much.

35:02.110 --> 35:04.110
What's the point of saying all that?

35:04.150 --> 35:05.000
If you're man enough,

35:05.000 --> 35:07.130
then love me openly and treat me right.

35:07.670 --> 35:09.140
I can carry your child.

35:09.800 --> 35:11.550
But I can't give birth to it in a gutter,

35:11.550 --> 35:12.880
or in a garbage dump.

35:14.790 --> 35:15.620
Nie Yucheng.

35:17.070 --> 35:18.440
I'm a normal woman too.

35:18.710 --> 35:20.140
I have dreams as well.

35:20.480 --> 35:21.280
I want to have a child.

35:21.280 --> 35:22.210
I want to have a home—

35:22.210 --> 35:23.920
a home together with you.

35:25.360 --> 35:26.960
Can you picture that future?

35:37.290 --> 35:38.390
[Customer Signature: Nie]

35:39.680 --> 35:40.890
[Customer Signature: Nie Yucheng]

35:42.190 --> 35:43.650
Go talk to the accountant.

35:51.550 --> 35:52.480
What do you mean?

35:52.710 --> 35:54.280
You know that's not what I want.

35:54.280 --> 35:55.480
You're at a critical stage in your career.

35:55.480 --> 35:56.480
Having a baby

35:56.480 --> 35:57.800
would only hold you back.

35:57.800 --> 36:00.200
It's a burden.
Have you thought about that?

36:02.320 --> 36:03.720
I get what you're saying.

36:03.760 --> 36:05.320
You're scared I'll use the baby
to threaten you.

36:05.320 --> 36:06.070
I'll go get

36:06.070 --> 36:07.590
an abortion right now,

36:07.960 --> 36:09.760
and cut ties with you forever.

36:23.840 --> 36:24.440
Zhenzhen.

36:28.000 --> 36:29.110
I'm married.

36:30.960 --> 36:33.230
You knew it from the start.

36:33.250 --> 36:35.210
Then why did you get involved with me?

36:35.210 --> 36:36.720
Am I your pet?

36:36.800 --> 36:37.710
Your prey?

36:38.280 --> 36:40.080
Or just something to throw away?

36:40.760 --> 36:41.560
None of those.

36:42.440 --> 36:43.040
Zhenzhen.

36:44.070 --> 36:45.270
I honestly don't know

36:46.220 --> 36:47.920
how it got to this point.

36:48.230 --> 36:49.310
And I have no idea

36:50.470 --> 36:51.630
what to do now.

36:56.670 --> 36:58.590
Don't always think the grass is greener
on the other side.

36:58.590 --> 37:00.190
You think walking away from this

37:00.190 --> 37:01.920
will lead to something better?

37:02.100 --> 37:03.830
It's like waiting for a bus.

37:03.850 --> 37:05.510
You wait forever, and it never comes.

37:05.510 --> 37:07.040
So you decide to take a taxi.

37:07.440 --> 37:09.110
But you can't get one
and you end up back in line again.

37:09.110 --> 37:10.110
Then you turn around

37:10.110 --> 37:12.000
and the bus is already gone.

37:12.000 --> 37:14.260
And you're right back where you started.

37:25.320 --> 37:28.380
Why is there suddenly
a hundred-person walking event?

37:28.800 --> 37:29.920
I told you to contact Director Zhang

37:29.920 --> 37:30.670
and sort this out!

37:30.670 --> 37:32.280
Did you even call him or not?

37:34.960 --> 37:37.960
Calling the Sports Bureau chief
is useless right now.

37:38.320 --> 37:40.720
Can you try the local government official?

37:40.920 --> 37:41.840
Enough! Cut the crap!

37:41.840 --> 37:43.170
Just do what I say, okay?

38:02.180 --> 38:03.640
Take your medicine first.

38:04.380 --> 38:06.710
There's millet porridge ready in the pot.

38:08.540 --> 38:09.800
Could you get me a bowl?

38:11.960 --> 38:12.670
Honey.

38:23.000 --> 38:24.880
I asked you to talk to the official.

38:24.880 --> 38:26.340
Did you get through or not?

38:27.280 --> 38:28.280
What do you mean?

38:43.220 --> 38:44.220
Come lie down.

38:49.110 --> 38:50.570
Take your medicine first.

39:08.800 --> 39:09.470
Here.

39:29.840 --> 39:30.550
Miyu.

39:31.890 --> 39:33.170
I'm so tired.

39:34.370 --> 39:35.370
I was thinking...

39:37.280 --> 39:38.680
if I didn't

39:38.700 --> 39:40.050
have to work,

39:40.670 --> 39:42.600
I could stay by your side every day.

39:43.520 --> 39:44.770
Even doing nothing,

39:45.700 --> 39:47.260
just lying here next to you—

39:48.280 --> 39:49.940
I'd be the happiest man alive.

40:00.150 --> 40:00.920
Miyu.

40:01.840 --> 40:03.900
Just keep taking care of me like this,

40:04.920 --> 40:06.180
for the rest of my life,

40:07.320 --> 40:08.190
will you?

40:10.730 --> 40:11.690
Stop talking.

40:17.380 --> 40:18.270
I know

40:19.190 --> 40:20.450
you're still mad at me,

40:21.320 --> 40:22.110
right?

40:30.560 --> 40:32.460
I know a lot has happened lately.

40:33.530 --> 40:35.660
It has made you

40:36.070 --> 40:37.270
worried and anxious.

40:37.270 --> 40:38.230
I'm sorry.

40:39.070 --> 40:40.280
It's my fault.

40:40.880 --> 40:42.810
I didn't give you enough security.

40:43.280 --> 40:45.280
But I really can't live without you.

40:45.460 --> 40:46.120
Miyu.

40:46.760 --> 40:48.160
Just think of it this way—

40:48.280 --> 40:49.710
you're stuck with me,

40:51.800 --> 40:53.280
and I'll never let you go.

40:55.710 --> 40:56.770
What about me then?

41:00.090 --> 41:01.490
Where does that leave me?

41:06.320 --> 41:07.780
You're always in my heart.

41:08.800 --> 41:09.840
I, Nie Yucheng,

41:10.280 --> 41:11.760
have worked hard all these years

41:11.760 --> 41:13.070
for only one reason—

41:15.310 --> 41:16.100
you.

41:22.630 --> 41:23.800
From now on,

41:24.690 --> 41:26.600
I won't let you get hurt.

41:27.280 --> 41:28.800
I'll protect you forever,

41:30.000 --> 41:31.800
and protect our family forever.

41:32.550 --> 41:33.400
I swear.

41:34.310 --> 41:35.430
Will you trust me?

41:45.750 --> 41:47.560
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

41:49.460 --> 41:51.340
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

41:52.830 --> 41:54.770
♪ People in the city ♪

41:55.540 --> 41:58.580
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

42:00.410 --> 42:02.030
♪ The palms of time ♪

42:04.130 --> 42:07.200
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

42:07.890 --> 42:10.810
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

42:11.850 --> 42:14.080
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

42:15.410 --> 42:18.440
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

42:19.120 --> 42:22.150
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

42:22.740 --> 42:25.860
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

42:26.600 --> 42:29.080
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

42:28.280 --> 42:29.190
Some people say

42:29.400 --> 42:31.400
lies make life better.

42:30.730 --> 42:33.880
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

42:31.960 --> 42:32.800
They're like candy

42:32.800 --> 42:35.070
wrapped in colorful cellophane.

42:34.500 --> 42:37.870
♪ The forgotten past ♪

42:35.590 --> 42:37.800
They let you live in false sweetness,

42:37.840 --> 42:40.110
so you don't have to face
the bitter truth.

42:38.850 --> 42:41.120
♪ There may be regrets ♪

42:41.360 --> 42:43.760
I know I'm lying to myself.

42:42.780 --> 42:45.020
♪ There may be loneliness ♪

42:44.150 --> 42:45.800
But sometimes,

42:45.800 --> 42:47.480
living in a world of lies

42:46.030 --> 42:49.330
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

42:47.920 --> 42:50.230
is the only way to feel happy.

42:49.760 --> 42:52.760
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

42:53.690 --> 42:56.680
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

42:57.440 --> 42:59.820
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

43:00.810 --> 43:04.130
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

43:04.840 --> 43:08.000
♪ The forgotten past ♪

43:10.350 --> 43:12.650
♪ Walking through this world ♪

43:13.720 --> 43:16.530
♪ Leaving no regrets behind ♪
